Eiwuang'ieki Osanduku lo Sotua te Kiriat-Yearim

(
2   Sam 
6  .
1  -
11  )


1  Neikilikuanishore apa Daudi ilarikok loo nkalifuni, o loo maa iip o pooki arikoni. 
2  Nejoki Daudi ina umata oo Siraeli, “Tenidolidolo intae eishiakino, naa tenaa eyieunoto o Olaitoriani Enkai ang, mairriwaki olkilikuai lelo alashera lang apa ootung'uaiyioki te nkop e Israel, o tenebo lelo apolosak ootii atua nena anas naata ndaat oo nchoo pee etum ninche aaetu tenebo enikitii. 
3  Naa manyaaki iyiook aayau osanduku le Nkai ene nikitii amu kitapalaitie apa too nkolong'i e Saul.” 
4  Nenyorraa ina umata pooki aas ina, amu eisidai apa ina bae too nkonyek o lorere.


5   Neiturrur apa Daudi Israel pooki ebaiki Shihor e Misiri o meetu enejing'ieki Hamat, pee eyau osanduku le Nkai te Kiriat-Yearim. 
6   Ore Daudi o ltung'ana le Israel pooki neilep aapuo Baala, aa taa Kiriat-Yearim natii Yuda, pee epuo aayau teine osanduku le Nkai, laa ninye eipotieki Olaitoriani oton te nchumata oo Lkerubi. 
7  Nenap ninche ilo sanduku le Nkai te ngarri ng'ejuk, aaitung'uaa enkaji e Aminadab, naa Usa, o Ahio apa ooreu ina garri. 
8  Ore Daudi o Siraeli pooki neshipa te dukuya Enkai te nkidimata enye pooki, to sinkolio, o to lwulul loo usin, o too nkai oo sinkolioitin, o too ndulen o too nkinantani dapashi o too ntarumpetani.


9  Ore ake pee ebau olkurroto oidong'ishoreki le Kidon, neiteleiki Usa enkaina enye ilo sanduku, amu etarrorre apa ilo kiteng, 
10  neyupuyup engoro o Laitoriani tialo Usa; neosh ninye tenkaraki naitorioyie enkaina enye aibung ilo sanduku; neye ninye teine te dukuya Enkai. 
11  Negoro Daudi enkaraki natarasaka Olaitoriani Usa; ore ine wueji neaku keji Peres Usa; o taata. 
12  Neureyu Daudi Olaitoriani oleng ina olong, nejo ninye, “Kaji nanu aiko tenayau osanduku le Nkai enkaji ai?” 
13  Neaku eitu eya Daudi ilo sanduku ang, atua enkanasa e Daudi, kake eibakibakie aya enkaji e Obed-edom le Giti. 
14   Neton ilo sanduku le Nkai te nkaji e Obed-edom ilapaitin okuni, nemayian Olaitoriani enkaji e Obed-edom o pooki toki naata.

